**Where to find things (use these; do not reinvent):**

| Need | Location |
|------|----------|
| Safe addresses for tests | `support/safes/safesHandler.js` ‚Üí `getSafes(CATEGORIES.static)`; fixtures in `fixtures/safes/` |
